    "en": {
      "name": "Comic Cat",
      "effect": "This card is treated as a Toon monster while \"Toon World\" is on the field. During the Main Phase (Quick Effect): You can Tribute 1 monster (if you control \"Toon World\", you can Tribute 1 monster your opponent controls, even though you do not control it), and if you do, Special Summon 1 monster that mentions \"Toon World\" from your hand or Deck, ignoring its Summoning conditions. You can only use this effect of \"Comic Cat\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
